%% wiki

Common Files
============

This document describes the file hirarchy of the framework's common files.

The following data needs to be organized:

- Melange's stylesheets. Importable with one single line of HTML code.
- Mootools' framework.
- Melange's core framework.
- Melange's ui framework. Importable with one single line of HTML code.
- Images.
- HTML files for tooltips, Thingy, Control Area and Containers.
